{"tid":667817,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：交警開咪提入錶 Benz男跳掣：除槍隻揪！","createTime":"2018-05-17T05:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T07:27:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d96c9d3c9a88a058f217f423b13508be41a7f553","tid":667817,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:28:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180517/20393345\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180517%2F20393345&d=c28YW418mKV8lj%2FngD5pWxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=1ca330f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180517%2F20393345&h=d203aef2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180517/20393345</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月17日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：交警開咪提入錶<br />\nBenz男跳掣：除槍隻揪！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180517/large/a1402a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180517%2Flarge%2Fa1402a.gif&h=f97fbba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■着藍色恤衫嘅平治車主不停指罵交警。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天口㷫，唔通人都躁啲？周一下晝5點幾，有位着淺藍色恤衫短褲嘅車主，揸住部白色Benz喺旺角弼街咪錶位泊車，懷疑佢冇入錶，結果俾巡邏嘅交通警員，開咪提佢要入番錶。點知呢位仁兄突然「跳掣」狂鬧阿Sir，唔單止粗口橫飛，仲挑釁阿Sir：「除咗支槍隻揪！」使唔使咁躁呀！<br />\n<br />\n咦！睇真啲，原來部Benz嘅車牌係「1 ON1」，唔通有所暗示？1 ON1係唔係隻揪隻咁解，可能要請教Ben Sir先知，但好彩嗰位阿Sir夠冷靜，一啲都冇勞氣。圍觀嘅途人都唔抵得Benz男所為，出聲幫阿Sir之餘，仲拍片3分鐘㖭!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180517/large/a1402b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180517%2Flarge%2Fa1402b.gif&h=77f0bc40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■交警表現冷靜，全程笑笑口。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n街坊：揸Benz就入錶啦<br />\n<br />\n從段片睇到，當時Benz男好唔滿意阿Sir叫佢入錶，大聲講：「啱啱泊好車咋嘛！」仲講晒粗口叫阿Sir「禮貌啲」。有街坊都睇唔過眼，出聲撐阿Sir，對住Benz男話：「睇咗你好耐啦，揸Benz就入錶啦!」<br />\n<br />\n佢哋拗咗一陣，Benz男又叫囂：「入咗30秒都唔夠，你咪抄囉，怕X啊？」阿Sir只係笑笑口話：「唔使入，怕咩箒，唔好震，又震啦先生」。Benz男即時㷫爆挑機：「一係你除咗支槍隻揪啦！」阿Sir就一於唔睬佢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到底平治最後有冇俾阿Sir抄牌呢？《蘋果》事後問過警方，警方就話當日大約5點15分，西九龍總區交通部人員喺旺角弼街巡邏，發現一部私家車冇畀咪錶費用，經過人員勸喻之後，嗰位司機畀番費用。不過警員發現部車嘅玻璃同車牌展示嘅形式，違反法例規定，警方稍後會向呢位司機發出「欠妥車輛報告」。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180517/large/a1402c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180517%2Flarge%2Fa1402c.gif&h=bb5abcde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n人稱太子安　出名唔入錶"},{"pid":"993b46151f256577f460b2b1948e82e2390b8e51","tid":667817,"uid":175934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:41:50.000Z","msg":"1 ON 1呢個車牌之前出街成日見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01275c937a3bc4a8ecbadc9396ccbea55764e367","tid":667817,"uid":70642,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:50:30.000Z","msg":"交警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192aaeb00fef5481e59d8cabb1253c9dcc5d04f6","tid":667817,"uid":183525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:23:00.000Z","msg":"智商說明一切.... <br />\n如果你有支槍, 仲點會放低支槍同你砌呢??"},{"pid":"71f5f46bf8b6a5bac5ec3ea73d114a61161d8430","tid":667817,"uid":154725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:24:36.000Z","msg":"唔好震，又震啦先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9f964a73204f363f993eb8ae325b44447c396b","tid":667817,"uid":1865,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:27:25.000Z","msg":"交乜撚警呀，打夠個通字好哂時間？<br />\n你會唔會叫機場特警叫機警呀屌你老母毒果。"},{"pid":"e5a42c2c2295f6a0158e9a46d09a7b2a1a7938ca","tid":667817,"uid":1865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:27:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>交乜撚警呀，打多個通字好哂時間？<br />\n你會唔會叫機場特警叫機警呀屌你老母毒果。</blockquote>"}]}